Changes included in the v3.0.2 release of SQLCipher for Android:

 * Add char[] for password to public interface to open database connections
 * Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/amplify-education/android-database-sqlcipher into amplify-education-master
 * Rebuild static openssl libraries from NDK r9c
 * Fix to use NDK r9c to build standalone toolchain
 * Add spacing in log messages for readability
 * Fix security issues where sensitive data is logged
 * Merge branch 'fixUbuntuBuild' of https://github.com/illarionov/android-sqlcipher-spatialite into illarionov-fixUbuntuBuild
 * Fix build when using Android NDK >= r9